oreground\"\n39:               >✓ Enrolled</span\n40:             >\n41:           </div>\n42:           <h2 class=\"text-[15px] font-semibold leading-snug group-hover:text-primary\">\n43:             {{ c.title }}\n44:           </h2>\n45:           <p class=\"text-[13px] text-muted-foreground mt-1 flex-1\">{{ c.short_introduction }}</p>\n46:           <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mt-3 text-[12px] text-muted-foreground\">\n47:             <span>📖 {{ c.lessons }} lessons</span>\n48:             <span>👤 {{ c.enrollments }}</span>\n49:           </div>\n50:           <div v-if=\"getEnrollment(c.id)\" class=\"mt-3\">\n51:             <div class=\"h-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary overflow-hidden\">\n52:               <div\n53:                 class=\"h-full bg-primary transition-all\"\n54:                 :style=\"{ width: `${courseProgressPercent(c.id)}%` }\"\n55:               />\n56:             </div>\n57:             <div class=\"text-[11px] text-muted-foreground mt-1\">\n58:               {{ courseProgressPercent(c.id) }}% complete\n59:             </div>\n60:           </div>\n61:         </RouterLink>\n62:       </div>\n63:     </div>\n64:   </AppLayout>\n65: </template>\n66: \n67: <script setup lang=\"ts\">\n68: import { computed } from \"vue\";\n69: import { RouterLink } from \"vue-router\";\n70: import AppLayout from \"@/components/AppLayout.vue\";\n71: import { getCourses, getEnrollment, courseProgressPercent } from \"@/data/store\";\n72: \n73: const courses = computed(() => getCourses());\n74: </script>\n\n(End of file - total 74 lines)\n</content>",
